text: Vommuli Island is an uninhabited island in the Maldives. It is located near a coral reef and has a sandy beach, with thick palm tree vegetation in its interior. The island is owned by Vermilion International, a company based in the Maldives. ==External links== *Commercial website describing island, from the island's owners Category:Uninhabited islands of the Maldives
title: Vonmuli
